contact: Stuart D. Bale (bale@berkeley.edu) @ UC Berkeley Space Sciences Laboratory

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Version
parameters.description: TDS wave-form burst telemetry format version number

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Burst_ID
parameters.description: Event number for this burst

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Burst_Quality
parameters.description: Overall quality for this burst (arbitrary units - used for burst selection)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_N_Samples_per_Channel
parameters.description: Number of samples per channel

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_N_Samples_per_Channel_MAX
parameters.description: Maximum number of samples allowed per channel (always 262,144)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Burst_Total_SWEAP_Counts
parameters.description: The total number of SWEAP particle counts in this TDS wave-form burst time series (Ch0) - the value is a positive integer (GE 0) returned as a real8 from the SWEAP particle counting channel (counts)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Burst_Total_SWEAP_Counting_Rate
parameters.description: The observed SWEAP particle counting rate (Ch0) during this burst (counts per second)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Trigger_Threshold_Engineering_mV
parameters.description: The current burst trigger threshold (engineering mV)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Trigger_Position
parameters.description: The desired time/location of the burst trigger after the start of the burst (s)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Sample_Speed
parameters.description: Possibly down-sampled sample rate of the TDS (Samples/second)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Sample_Period
parameters.description: Possibly down-sampled sample period of the TDS samples (seconds/sample)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_Burst_Period
parameters.description: Burst duration period of this TDS burst (seconds/burst)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_DFB_Voltage_V1
parameters.description: The DFB DC voltage measurement from the V1 sensor (Volts)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_DFB_Voltage_V2
parameters.description: The DFB DC voltage measurement from the V2 sensor (Volts)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_DFB_Voltage_V3
parameters.description: The DFB DC voltage measurement from the V3 sensor (Volts)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_DFB_Voltage_V4
parameters.description: The DFB DC voltage measurement from the V4 sensor (Volts)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_SC_Reaction_Wheel_Speed_RW1
parameters.description: Indicates the rotational speed of the 1st reaction wheel (revolutions per second)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_SC_Reaction_Wheel_Speed_RW2
parameters.description: Indicates the rotational speed of the 2nd reaction wheel (revolutions per second)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_SC_Reaction_Wheel_Speed_RW3
parameters.description: Indicates the rotational speed of the 3rd reaction wheel (revolutions per second)

parameters.name: PSP_FLD_L2_TDS_WF_SC_Reaction_Wheel_Speed_RW4
parameters.description: Indicates the rotational speed of the 4th reaction wheel (revolutions per second)
